data.title: Schedule at a Glance
data.meta_description: View InfoComm 2024 education sessions, networking events, tours, CTS training session, and more!
data.text:
AVIXA Training Courses

AVIXA Training Courses, designated by the "TD" in the session ID, are three-day courses from 8 a.m.-5 p.m. from Saturday, June 08 to Monday, June 10. These sessions are available for individual purchase during registration.

Member Price Non-Member Price $1,999 $2,499

Two Day Courses

Member Price Non-Member Price $1,299 $1,699

One Day Courses

Member Price Non-Member Price $649 $799

Technical Workshops

Technical Workshops, designated by "PW" in the session ID, consist of two to four hours of dedicated instruction on a single topic. These sessions are available for individual purchase during registration.

Member Price Non-Member Price $249 $299

InfoComm Education Pass

NOTE: The Education Pass always includes the Manufacturers' Training Pass, the Exhibit Hall Pass and access to Audio Demo Rooms. Manufacturers' Training Pass included in Education Pass and Single Session Pass. The Exhibit Hall & Audio Demo rooms are included in the Education Pass

Member Price Non-Member Price Individual Session $159 $199 InfoComm Education Pass $599 $749

Manufacturers' Training Pass

Manufacturers' Training sessions are designated by "MT" in the session ID. These sessions are included in the other passes listed above or can be purchased separately. Manufacturers' Training sessions are not available for individual purchase.

Member Price Non-Member Price $99 $149

Integrated Experience Tours

Integrated Experience Tours, designated by "EX" in the session ID, are offsite tours of local pro AV installations. These tours can be purchased individually during registration.

Member Price Non-Member Price $299 $399

SAVe Certification Workshop

Member Price Non-Member Price $499 $599

HETMA Higher Education Summit

Member Price Non-Member Price $349 $449

NSCA BizSkills

Member Price Non-Member Price $299 $359

Market Insight Lunches

Member Price Non-Member Price $129 $149

Congreso pricing

Member Price Non-Member Price $99 $149

Networking Events

There are various networking events available to attend where you can meet like-minded AV professionals and catch up with colleagues. See member and non-member prices listed in each networking event description.

Show Floor Tours

Show Floor Tours, designated by "SF" in the session ID, are tours within the exhibit hall. Tour topics are Digital Signage, Learning Spaces, Conferencing and Collaboration, Audio, Enterprise IT, and Content Production and Streaming.

Member Price Non-Member Price $99 $149

Exhibit Hall Pass

Access the Exhibit Hall and Audio Demo Rooms with the Exhibit Hall Pass. This Pass is included with all education purchases.

Member Price Non-Member Price Free $399

Free Sessions - Xchange Live & Technology Innovation Stage

Free sessions are available in the Exhibit Hall at the Xchange Live booth, designated by "XL", and at the Technology Innovation Stage, designated by "TI" in the session ID.
